#RubyPost 0.0.5 README

You can download the latest version of rubypost from rubyforge. Type:

gem install rubypost

Or download the source and run rake to build the gem, then install the gem into your ruby installation.

This version of rubypost implements most of the basic metapost features.  See the test files for usage examples. 

